# random number generation test

+ pulse clock
= 250 clock@rate

+ random rnd
> clock@out rnd@clock

+ map scale
= 0 scale@imin
= 1 scale@imax
= 100 scale@omin
= 800 scale@omax
> rnd@out scale@in

+ sinosc osc
> scale@out osc@freq

+ mult amp
> osc@out amp@in1
= 0.8 amp@in2

> amp@out out@l
> amp@out out@r

